| **H2: Validity** | Scores show expected correlational patterns. | ‚úÖ **Supported** | The correlation matrix revealed strong, theoretically-consistent relationships. Ex: `Liberty/Oppression` (r=0.87), `Harm/Cheating` (r=0.84), `Loyalty/Cheating` (r=-0.66). |
